column2: SELECT top #  p.objID,p.ra,p.dec,p.dered_u,p.dered_g,p.dered_r,p.dered_i,p.dered_z,  s.specobjid, s.class, s.z, g.specObjID,  g.h_beta_flux, g.oiii_#_flux, g.h_alpha_flux, g.nii_#_flux from PhotoObjAll AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objID  JOIN galSpecLine AS g ON p.objID = g.specObjID  WHERE   s.z BETWEEN # AND #  AND s.class=GALAXY&&&
